00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:31,540
♪Not knowing where to go♪

3
00:00:31,780 --> 00:00:36,540
♪The moonlight tonight feels sorrowful♪

4
00:00:39,380 --> 00:00:42,260
♪I stand alone against it♪

5
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:44,620
♪But I don't want to♪

6
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:50,780
♪The longing catches me off guard♪

7
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:58,380
♪To the silent night, I surrender myself♪

8
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:01,500
♪Tossing and turning, lost in confusion♪

9
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:10,620
♪In the darkness, I lose my way

10
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:32,940
[Bound by Sin]

11
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:35,980
[Episode 16]

12
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,350
Yingxian!

13
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:53,760
Do you know

14
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:55,640
that he has been lying to you?

15
00:01:58,590 --> 00:01:59,760
20 years ago,

16
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,070
he was the young master of the Gu family.

17
00:02:02,350 --> 00:02:03,920
After the Gu family was wiped out by enemies,

18
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,200
the butler, Fu Beihai, adopted him

19
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,870
and changed his name to Fu Cheng.

20
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:10,910
They have always thought

21
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:13,520
that the Jiang family took all of the Gu family's assets.

22
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,840
So, they approached you

23
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:17,680
to recover the same.

24
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:18,470
Yingxian,

25
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:19,910
hear me out.

26
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,120
It's not what you think.

27
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,430
There's no need to explain.

28
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,280
Are you trying to say that you have no ulterior motives

29
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,910
by approaching Yingxian?

30
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,310
Or are you trying to say

31
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,680
that your name isn't Fu Cheng?

32
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:37,560
Yingxian,

33
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,800
you cannot marry him.

34
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:41,190
If you marry him,

35
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:44,000
you're letting them get away with their plan.

36
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,520
Mr. Shen.

37
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,000
I take note of what you just told me.

38
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,960
Thank you for making your way here to inform me.

39
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,400
Yingxian.

40
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,190
You don't believe me.

41
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:02,840
I believe you.

42
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:06,190
Everything is clearly written

43
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,400
