44
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:09,430
I will deal with the rest myself.

45
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:11,910
I don't want to trouble you, Mr. Shen.

46
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,360
Fine.

47
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,240
I'm leaving.

48
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:28,360
Yingxian.

49
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:30,630
We...

50
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,680
We're breaking up

51
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:34,120
because it is the best option

52
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,840
for both the Jiang and Shen families in the current situation.

53
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,520
It has nothing to do with other people.

54
