♪Aren't you the one♪

57
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:25,720
♪Who pretends to be a stranger after falling in love?♪

58
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:29,920
♪I'm torn, not knowing what to choose♪

59
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:33,240
♪Giving up and then picking it up again♪

60
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,720
♪What more do you want from me?♪

61
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:39,760
♪If it's not enough, I'll fill it with persistence♪

62
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:44,440
♪How do I describe your silhouette?♪

63
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:48,400
♪All you gave me was a love out of sync♪

64
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:51,600
♪The marks left behind are being pulled♪

65
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:55,280
♪And finally torn apart♪

66
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:59,440
♪The fireworks cool the loneliness♪

67
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:03,240
♪Yet you ask me to keep safe♪

68
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:07,040
♪All my memories of you♪

69
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:09,950
Shen Dongyang wouldn't investigate Fu Cheng for no reason.

70
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:11,720
Go and find out

71
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,560
