72
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:16,680
Find out who made him so interested in Fu Cheng.

73
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,040
Boss.

74
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:20,800
Only those in the family know

75
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,950
