76
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,750
No one else but his sister

77
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,310
knows so much

78
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:26,240
about Fu Cheng's situation.

79
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,560
I knew it was Fu Zhi's doing,

80
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:32,310
but I need more concrete evidence.

81
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,630
In that case,

82
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:36,190
do we need to verify

83
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,830
whether the information is true?

84
00:05:40,190 --> 00:05:41,430
Judging from his reaction today,

85
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:43,600
it's obvious that it is true.

86
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:49,000
Boss,

87
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:50,920
what will you do?

88
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,270
I think

89
00:05:56,510 --> 00:05:57,720
he had an ulterior motive

90
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:00,040
when he first approached me.

91
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:02,870
Later,

92
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,600
he probably discovered

93
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,750
that we were not related to the Gu family.

94
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:12,310
Furthermore, he has fallen in love with me.

95
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,360
So, he is sincere

96
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,270
about being with me right now.

97
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:22,060
♪All my memories of you♪

98
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:25,620
♪Since I've loved, I have no choice♪

99
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,780
♪A firework♪

100
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:29,900
♪Needs a promise to fall perfectly♪

101
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:33,860
♪Only the heartbroken understand the marks left behind♪

102
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:36,180
♪Excuses aren't lacking♪

103
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:40,740
♪But only those who've loved have the right to remain silent...♪

104
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:44,310
Do you trust him that much, Boss?

105
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,270
Not really.

106
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,430
I just want to give him a chance to explain.

107
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:56,000
Forget about Fu Cheng for now

108
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,480
and investigate Shen Dongyang.

109
00:06:58,870 --> 00:06:59,630
I'm worried

110
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,270
that he might do something else.

111
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:03,870
Don't worry, Boss.

112
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:06,100
♪Excuses aren't lacking♪

113
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:10,780
♪But only those who've loved have the right to remain silent♪

114
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:14,900
♪It's not that I talk endlessly to push away your reluctance...♪

115
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,390
Cheng.

116
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:21,830
I should have

117
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,480
told her sooner.

118
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:27,430
Cheng.

119
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,480
Don't be like this.

120
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,270
She's not worth it.

121
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,270
