124
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,390
She is not related

125
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:38,480
to the annihilation of the Gu family.

126
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,950
Even if she didn't do it,

127
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,360
