128
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:46,360
She should be responsible for everything the Jiang family did.

129
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:48,270
The Jiang family

130
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,830
has nothing to do with what happened back then.

131
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,070
It was your father

132
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,240
who accidentally leaked information

133
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:04,560
about the Gu family to the enemies

134
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:07,270
which caused the Gu family to be wiped out.

135
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,720
The Jiang family only used the opportunity

136
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:15,310
to acquire most of the Gu family's assets at a low price.

137
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:19,070
Jiang Zhen took advantage of the situation,

138
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:23,070
but he didn't do anything harmful.

139
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,870
Impossible.

140
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,510
My father...

141
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,680
My father said it was the Jiang family.

142
00:08:34,550 --> 00:08:36,630
I think Uncle Fu felt very guilty,

143
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,720
and it turned into a grudge.

144
00:08:43,910 --> 00:08:46,200
However, he couldn't abandon both of us.

145
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,510
So, he put the blame

146
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:52,240
on the Jiang family,

147
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,200
who gained the most out of this.

148
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:57,670
He lied to us

149
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,080
and lied to himself.

150
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,360
It's all my fault.

151
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,240
If I hadn't exposed his lies,

152
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,640
he wouldn't have committed suicide.

153
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:15,480
I've let him down.

154
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,550
Why did this happen?

155
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,960
This shouldn't have happened.

156
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:26,120
Zhi.

157
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,790
Return to Jiang Mansion for now.

158
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,750
I'm going to find Yingxian.

159
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,750
I want to make it clear to her.

160
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:41,240
I want to make it clear to her.

161
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:47,750
Cheng.

162
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,120
Jiang Yingxian.

163
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,630
I don't care if there's a grudge between you and the Gu family.

164
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,720
You caused my father's death

165
00:09:56,910 --> 00:09:58,440
and stole Fu Cheng away from me.

166
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,360
You've been enjoying life for many years

167
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,600
as the heiress of a rich family.

168
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,870
It's time for you to lose everything.

169
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,320
Fu Cheng, there's a new mission.

170
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:15,150
You are required to return to the camp with me.

171
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,150
We must depart immediately.

172
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:17,000
Cheng.

173
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,600
Since you are busy,

174
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,550
you should return to the camp with this officer.

175
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,790
I will explain it to Yingxian for you.

176
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,030
All right.

177
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,440
Zhi.

178
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,870
You must help me clear things up.

179
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,390
Let's go.

180
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:50,000
What?

181
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,320
He left without saying a word?

182
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:53,670
The person following Fu Zhi said

183
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:55,840
someone picked up Fu Cheng and left the city.

184
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:58,670
What is Fu Zhi doing now?

185
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:00,000
Fu Zhi is meeting someone

186
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,030
but I'm not sure who she will be meeting.

187
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:19,360
Hello.

188
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,360
This is the Jiang Mansion.

189
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,360
Mr. Yingqi?

190
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:24,600
What? You're back?

191
00:11:26,270 --> 00:11:27,390
If Miss Jiang finds out,

192
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,150
