193
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,720
All right.

194
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:33,840
I'll send it to you right away.

195
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:36,630
However, you must tell Miss Jiang.

196
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:38,960
Otherwise, I can't help you.

197
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:40,600
All right.

198
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:01,550
Hello. Is this the Bureau of Telecommunication?

199
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,550
Can you help me check

200
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:05,200
