201
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:09,120
Yes. The previous call.

202
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:19,630
Hello.

203
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,240
Is it Mr. Jiang?

204
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,790
It has been so long, Mr. Jiang.

205
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:45,960
Are you the one who asked me to meet you here?

206
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:48,320
Do we know each other?

207
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:49,870
I am Fu Zhi.

208
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,840
Fu Zhi?

209
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:54,960
It sounds familiar.

210
00:12:57,750 --> 00:12:59,270
Were you the one at Haicheng the other day?

211
00:13:00,270 --> 00:13:00,840
It's me.

212
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,910
Why are you looking for me?

213
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,600
Yingxian should have

214
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,630
