217
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,840
You're mistaken, Mr. Jiang.

218
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,200
I came to find you

219
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,630
because I want to work with you.

220
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,360
Work with me?

221
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:19,030
