222
00:13:19,510 --> 00:13:21,240
Miss Jiang sent you abroad

223
00:13:21,670 --> 00:13:22,870
yet you came back in secret

224
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,270
because you wanted

225
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,390
to be the head of the Jiang family.

226
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:30,960
Are you trying to tell me

227
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:31,480
that you can help me

228
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:33,200
become the head?

229
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,440
I can help you indeed.

230
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,080
What do you want from me?

231
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:46,480
Are you trying to become my wife?

232
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,910
You are overthinking, Mr. Jiang.

233
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,790
I just want Miss Jiang

234
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,320
to stop clinging to my brother.

235
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:54,840
Your brother?

236
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:57,960
Who is your brother?

237
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:58,670
Fu Cheng.

238
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,790
Fu Cheng...

239
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,030
My sister's handsome bodyguard?

240
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:09,030
