241
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,240
She must be out of her mind.

242
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,270
Anyway,

243
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,200
I am the only person who can help you now.

244
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:53,540
♪I often think of the last time we met♪

245
00:14:54,020 --> 00:14:59,220
♪You stood before me with a real smile♪

246
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:04,460
♪I was a little restless♪

247
